text: Dad Khan Jarwar is a town and Union Council of Tando Allahyar District in the Sindh Province of Pakistan. It has 65,295 people. It is part of Chamber Taluka. It is in the south of the district at 25°19'5N 68°43'20E.Location of Dad Khan Jarwar- Falling Rain Genomics ==References== Category:Union councils of Tando Allahyar District
